Roux P., 2021. – Description d’une nouvelle Nebria de Chine (Coleoptera, Caraboidea, Nebriidae). Bulletin de la Société entomologique de France, 126 (1) : 12‑14 doi : 10.32475/bsef_2160.

Abstract. – Description of a new Nebria from China (Coleoptera‚ Caraboidea‚ Nebriidae). Nebria (Asionebria) ledouxi n. sp. is described from China (Tibet). It presents all the characters of the subgenus Asionebria and is particularly close to Nebria mentonincisa. It is dedicated to Georges Ledoux.

